videos.description: Baylor's Manu Lecomte gets the steal and finishes the tough layup on the other end.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lecomte gets the steal and scores the tough layup

videos.description: Landen Lucas misses the shot but Josh Jackson slams it home.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson hammers home the put back dunk

videos.description: Scott Drew happy with the way his defense played in the first half but he wants to keep Kansas  out of transition in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Baylor coach Scott Drew on the Bears 1st half performance

videos.description: Frank Mason gets the steal and passes it to Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk who hits the open 3-pointer
videos.headline: Kansas gets the steal and it leads to an open 3-pointer

videos.description: Frank Mason goes end to end and hits the running layup to cap off a 13-0 for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Frank Mason hits floater to cap off 13-0 run for Kansas

videos.description: Josh Jackson misses the free throw, gets his own miss and passes it to Devonte Graham for the 3- pointer.
videos.headline: Jackson's headsup play leads to Kansas 3

videos.description: Josh Jackson pump fakes, drives base line and slams it home for the dunk.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson pumps and hammers home the dunk

videos.description: Josh Jackson breaks down his big game and the big 2nd half for Kansas as they beat Baylor.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson on his big game in the win against Baylor
